This paper is primarily focused on reinforcement learning, which falls under the category of machine learning. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper deals with robotics environments, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.RO (Robotics). The paper also uses deep learning techniques, which could place it in cs.CV (Computer Vision) or cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper deals with control systems, which could place it in cs.SY (Systems and Control).
